statements.sql: select `posts`.`id`, `channels`.`name` as `channel_name`, `channels`.`logo` as `channel_logo`, `channels`.`slug` as `channel_slug`, `topics`.`name` as `topic_name`, `posts`.`title`, `posts`.`type`, `posts`.`slug`, `posts`.`image`, `posts`.`video_thumb`, `posts`.`video`, `posts`.`description`, `posts`.`status`, `posts`.`publish_date`, `posts`.`view_count`, `posts`.`reaction`, `posts`.`shere`, `posts`.`comment`, `posts`.`favorite`, `posts`.`resource` from `posts` inner join `channels` on `posts`.`channel_id` = `channels`.`id` inner join `topics` on `posts`.`topic_id` = `topics`.`id` where `posts`.`slug` = 'video-post' limit 1

select `name`, count(*) as count from `reactions` inner join `reactables` on `reactions`.`id` = `reactables`.`reaction_id` where `reactables`.`reactable_id` = 1049 and `reactables`.`reactable_type` = 'App\\Models\\Post' group by `name`
select * from `post_views` where `post_id` = 1049 and `user_id` is null limit 1
select * from `posts` where `id` < 1049 order by `id` desc limit 1
select * from `posts` where `id` > 1049 order by `id` asc limit 1

select `posts`.`id`, `channels`.`name` as `channel_name`, `channels`.`logo` as `channel_logo`, `channels`.`slug` as `channel_slug`, `topics`.`name` as `topic_name`, `posts`.`title`, `posts`.`type`, `posts`.`slug`, `posts`.`image`, `posts`.`video_thumb`, `posts`.`video`, `posts`.`description`, `posts`.`status`, `posts`.`publish_date`, `posts`.`view_count`, `posts`.`reaction`, `posts`.`shere`, `posts`.`comment`, `posts`.`favorite`, `posts`.`resource` from `posts` inner join `channels` on `posts`.`channel_id` = `channels`.`id` inner join `topics` on `posts`.`topic_id` = `topics`.`id` where `topics`.`name` = 'Entertainment' and `posts`.`slug` != 'video-post' and `posts`.`id` not in (1048, null) order by `posts`.`publish_date` desc limit 4
